    "name": "Mesh Independence Study for VAD CFD Model",
    "description": "A structured mesh refinement study was conducted across three grid levels (coarse, medium, fine) to assess discretization sensitivity of hemolysis index predictions. The study applied the Grid Convergence Index (GCI) method per Celik et al. (2008) to quantify numerical uncertainty in wall shear stress and scalar transport fields.",
    "activityType": "MeshRefinementVerification"
  },
