      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant physics; formal change management process required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM 9) is version-controlled and regression tests exist for basic flow cases, but no hemolysis-specific regression suite is maintained. Change management documentation is informal. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstrated order-of-accuracy verification for all governing equations relevant to hemolysis transport using manufactured solutions or benchmark problems with known analytical solutions.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were performed for the Navier-Stokes solver but not for the scalar hemolysis transport equation or the power-law damage accumulation model. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
