    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite Model Risk Level 5 requirements, the credibility assessment package is accepted for submission. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated; 7 factors are formally assessed with documented rationale, and 6 factors are flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. The mesh independence study activity was registered in the assessment plan and executed; discretization uncertainty estimates are documented. The overall package meets minimum documentation standards for regulatory submission, acknowledging that achieved credibility levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors.",
